The proposed fix is to alter the INFO level log message to:

{code}
Snapshot snap-00000000 exceeds global total snapshot size limit of 50GB (see storage.global_total_snapshot_size_limit_gb configurable property)
{code}

The log message is now:

{code}
2015-02-23 22:36:33  INFO 000025072 BlockStorageController   | Snapshot snap-6cfdc74b exceeds global total snapshot size limit of 3GB (see storage.global_total_snapshot_size_limit_gb configurable property)
{code}
